CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Lunai Bioworks Inc. is a pre-clinical stage biotechnology firm developing medicine, diagnostics, and biodefense products, operating mostly in the United States and the Netherlands. It specializes in AI-driven drug discovery and is advancing allogeneic dendritic cell therapeutic vaccines for solid tumors and breast cancer, as well as AI-based early cancer detection platforms.
